    {
      "segment_id": 3,
      "original_text": "לְכׇל אַחַת וְאַחַת. אָמַר רַב יְהוּדָה אָמַר שְׁמוּאֵל: כְּלָלוֹ שֶׁל רַבִּי מֵאִיר – פְּרָטוֹ שֶׁל רַבִּי יְהוּדָה; כְּלָלוֹ שֶׁל רַבִּי יְהוּדָה – פְּרָטוֹ שֶׁל רַבִּי מֵאִיר.",
      "reconstructed_text": "לְכׇל אַחַת וְאַחַת. אָמַר רַב יְהוּדָה אָמַר שְׁמוּאֵל: – כְּלָלוֹ שֶׁל – פְּרָטוֹ שֶׁל",
      "reconstructed_html": "לְכׇל אַחַת וְאַחַת. אָמַר רַב יְהוּדָה אָמַר שְׁמוּאֵל: <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"medium\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Shevuot 38a:4:1\" data-marker=\"לא גרסינן\" data-original=\"כְּלָלוֹ\">כְּלָלוֹ</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"medium\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Shevuot 38a:4:1\" data-marker=\"לא גרסינן\" data-original=\"שֶׁל\">שֶׁל</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"medium\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Shevuot 38a:4:1\" data-marker=\"לא גרסינן\" data-original=\"רַבִּי\">רַבִּי</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"medium\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Shevuot 38a:4:1\" data-marker=\"לא גרסינן\" data-original=\"מֵאִיר\">מֵאִיר</span> – <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"medium\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Shevuot 38a:4:1\" data-marker=\"לא גרסינן\" data-original=\"פְּרָטוֹ\">פְּרָטוֹ</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"medium\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Shevuot 38a:4:1\" data-marker=\"לא גרסינן\" data-original=\"שֶׁל\">שֶׁל</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"medium\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Shevuot 38a:4:1\" data-marker=\"לא גרסינן\" data-original=\"רַבִּי\">רַבִּי</span> <span class=\"girsa-change girsa-deletion\" data-change-type=\"deletion\" data-confidence=\"medium\" data-source=\"rashi_girsa\" data-source-ref=\"Rashi on Shevuot 38a:4:1\" data-marker=\"לא גרסינן\" data-original=\"יְהוּדָה;\">יְהוּדָה;</